Cell.Text: Let's see here...
[S] Yeah, got this note.
I have a letter here from Quintus Navale in Windhelm. He said it was urgent.
[E] I've got a letter and a lot of gold. Something about it being your inheritance? Oh, and... sorry for your loss.
A letter... not sure who from. He wouldn't say. Just that he was a friend of yours.
[S] I have a letter here for you.
A note from someone named Calcelmo, in Markarth.
It's from... Falk Firebeard at the Blue Palace? You've got friends in high places.
There's a new museum opening up in Dawnstar. The owner is asking me to hand out invitations to travelers.
[S] Got this from a pretty excited looking dark elf around Raven Rock. He said it was important I got it to you as soon as I could.
[S] Another note from your friend Ralis. I hope everything is all right.
[S] Another letter from Ralis. He's starting to scare me a little.
[S] I've got another letter from Ralis, but this is the last thing I'm delivering for him. That place is just too much for me.
Here's a letter from the Jarl's steward. Looks like official business.
There's a new lady in charge of the Orphanage in Riften. She asked me to hand out these notices to everyone I met.
Ah, a letter from the Jarl! Moving up in the world, eh?
[S] G|[E] Looks like that's it. Got to go.
[S] [E] I've been looking for you. Got something I'm supposed to deliver - your hands only.
G|Nope, sorry. Nothing.

Node.Caption: WICourierTopic: Do you have anything for me?

Cell.Text: From who?
[S] [E] Don't know. Creepy fella, black robe. Couldn't see his face. Paid me a pretty sum to get that into your hands, though.
